summary: Adds a player home on a small island near Winterhelm, its located next to a waterfall. Doesn\'t require any DLC\'s just skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
Adds a player home on a small island near Winterhelm, its located next to a waterfall.

Comes complete with its own bridge, lookout tower (for the views) and own pier (for some fishing). It has an outside crafting area, inside has everything you need including kitchen, bedroom, storage room and basement (not started yet, just bare atm). 

Has working mannequins (2 atm will add more) working bookshelf\'s, and loads of storage barrels and chests.

Chickens? ...Yes those too!
author: kobra8four
